---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Pauls Technical Services" description="About Paul: AI Administrator and Microsoft 365 / Azure solution builder.">
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 24px;">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">about</p>
      <h1>Hello, I'm Paul.</h1>
      <p class="lede muted">
        I run Pauls Technical Services, an IT services and consulting practice.
        My background is enterprise Microsoft 365 administration; my present is
        building AI agent solutions on Copilot and Azure — and writing about
        it as I go.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="border-top: none; padding-top: 12px;">
    <div class="wrap" style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2>What I do</h2>
      <p>
        I work as a programmer and AI Administrator within an enterprise
        Microsoft 365 tenant, and deliver end-to-end solutions for clients —
        from business requirements and cost estimation through architecture,
        prototype, and proposal.
      </p>

      <h2>What I write about</h2>
      <p>
        Copilot agent building (declarative and custom engine), agent licensing
        and the Copilot Credits model, the Retrieval API, Copilot Studio, the
        Microsoft 365 Agents SDK, Azure AI Foundry, and the governance side:
        Entra Agent ID, Purview, and Defender.
      </p>

      <h2>Contributors</h2>
      <p>
        This site also publishes articles from invited contributors — friends
        and colleagues building in the same space. Every article carries its
        author's byline. If you'd like to write here, get in touch.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        The fastest ways to reach me are
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/" rel="me">LinkedIn</a> or
        <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">email</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
